comments: Brogdon (INID) briefly wraps Wood (HOU) as he is rolling to the basket, but the contact is marginal and does not affect his FOM.
Bitadze (IND) is set in Porter Jr.'s (HOU) path and absorbs the contact during the screen attempt.
Brissett (IND) alongside of Wood's (HOU) path and makes marginal contact that does not affect his FOM before the screen attempt.
Tate (HOU) makes contact with Bitadze's (IND) head during his shot attempt.
Bitadze (IND) makes marginal contact with Wood's (HOU) arm as he makes a move towards the rim.
Wood (HOU) gathers the ball and shuffles his feet during his shot attempt near the rim.
Brissett (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from Wood (HOU). Any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Tate (HOU) makes marginal contact with Bitadze (IND) while boxing out during the rebound.
Tate (HOU) briefly places his hand on Brogdon's (IND) arm before the screen attempt and the contact is marginal.
Christopher (HOU) makes contact with Bitadze's (IND) arm that affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Bitadze (IND) dislodges Christopher (HOU) during the rebound attempt.
Taylor (IND) remains in a legally obtained rebounding position and the contact with Wood (HOU) is marginal.  Wood then pulls Taylor to the floor as the take foul is whistled.
Porter Jr. (HOU) commits a take foul against Hield (IND).
Mathews (HOU) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Wood (HOU) extends an arm towards Brogdon (IND) during the screen but the contact is marginal.
Christopher (HOU) commits a personal take foul against Hield (IND).
